organic.title: Parkway General Surgeons: Home
organic.snippet: Parkway General Surgeons is located in Bellingham, Washington. We have two Board Certified general surgeons: Dr. Keith VanderGriend and Dr. Camille Miller.

organic.title: Meet our Surgeons - Parkway General Surgeons
organic.snippet: Our surgeons – Keith VanderGriend, MD, FACS and Camille Miller, MD, FACS – are trained in a variety of procedures best-suited for your individual needs.
